Harpy
The old necromancer experimented with a harpy a long time ago. But now he does not want others to use the results of those experiments. So he wishes the harpy killed and promises a handsome reward for the job.
#subobj  1
Find the Harpy
The Harpy you must kill lives in the south west sector of the desert of the Necromancer. Exercise caution....mayhap other dangerous creatures lurk near her den!
#subobj  2
Kill the Harpy
You must destroy her. T'would help if you deal with other local creatures first before you start your fight with the Harpy.
